## How to Run

```bash
# Option 1 — just open it
open rps-arena.html

# Option 2 — serve locally (optional)
npx serve .
# or
python -m http.server 8000
```

No build step. No npm install. No config.

---

## Game Logic

Standard Rock Paper Scissors rules:

- Rock beats Scissors
- Scissors beats Paper
- Paper beats Rock

The bot picks randomly each round. Scores, win rate, and streak are tracked in memory for the session.

---

## Browser Support

Works in all modern browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge). Requires Canvas 2D API support — available in every browser released after 2012.

